      "description": "This exquisite vehicle represents the absolute pinnacle of pride of ownership. Finished in a stunning, deep metallic paint that has been professionally ceramic coated, the exterior is entirely free of stone chips, swirl marks, or imperfections, gleaming with a mirror-like finish. It has been strictly garage-kept and has never seen a car wash brush, having been exclusively hand-washed. Inside, the cabin is a time capsule; the premium leather upholstery remains supple and matte, with no visible bolster wear or creasing, and the original factory protective films are still present on several trim pieces. Every switch, button, and feature\u2014including the premium surround-sound system and panoramic sunroof\u2014operates with tactile precision. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, featuring a comprehensive, documentable service history from a single authorized dealership. Recently fitted with a fresh set of high-performance tires and having just undergone a rigorous multi-point inspection, this car drives with the tightness and responsiveness of a brand-new vehicle. This is a rare opportunity for a discerning buyer to acquire a collector-grade example that is indistinguishable from one on a showroom floor.",
